  "purpose": "Provider lifecycle for design token resolution Wraps the base \n DesignToken concept with initialization , plugin registry integration , \n and active theme management Framework specific UI adapters ( React \n Context , CompositionLocal , NativeScript globals ) consume this \n provider for token resolution and theme switching"
